Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今曰天睛夹有炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可视度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以牙还牙以血洗血纷争不断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想着总算解决了协约联合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却回到了没曰没夜的最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旁边正睡着的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上醒来身首异处也是常事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是莱茵战线的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大队听令 进行支援战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能低空突破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作气消灭敌军炮兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行对空对魔导行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们突击后友军的炮击不会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不觉得队中会有蠢货被友军击中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且留意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声势一如既往的大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮弹又不是不要钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮弹为了空中爆炸采用了定时信管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂出的碎片会像雨一样袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是05
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个敌魔导中队进入可视范围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一中队进行对魔导师战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那群蠢猪打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人对付步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速解决后汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大队诸位 开始热闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必很愉悦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以叫你不要松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多亏这样赚到了击坠数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也请期待我的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心最后一次击坠数变成自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没被大队长教育够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学学人家谢列布里亚科夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是跟着大队长一起飞就自然变成老司机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉你和大队长搭档很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实可以这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我和您换一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军务上可是没法交换昵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾没法一起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德古雷查夫少校！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问德古雷查夫少校在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是副指挥官怀斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紧急军情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\frz-90\pos(722,362)}第八话 火的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后方地区被截断了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丽娜市的当地抵抗组织蜂起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丽娜市原本是共和国领土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埋了下个隐患吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驻军的宪兵镇压失败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁路已经被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通往前线的运输也受到阻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没饭没弹药还谈什么打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.18,In,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(642,546)}帝国领土             阿丽娜市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人空降！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共和国正开展空降作战！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌魔导师正和叛徒们汇合…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.84,In,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,504)}赛弗连·比安特中校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制桥头堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好长期战准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能拖延战局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饿死帝国军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 德古雷查夫少校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日14：23起 方面军司令部下达了特令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二〇三大队迅速歼灭与阿丽娜市叛徒汇合的敌魔导师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成后与友军进行市区镇压作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态刻不容缓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是命令 我非常乐意执行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但城市战很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参谋本部已立案了一套短时间内镇压市区敌军的作战方针
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请向是何方案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即对阿丽娜市发布避难通告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布后 仍留在市内的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将遵照国际法全部被视为共和国部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上头的命令是消灭市内所有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歼灭敌魔导部队后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮兵将进行炮击轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进退皆为地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来 请恕我问一个无关紧要的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的敌人仅仅只是共和国军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是理所当然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽可能告知我能够预知的敌军战力构成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了少数共和国魔导师以外都是民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有不少帝国子民成为了俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须立即展开行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过普通市民倒是会成为制约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人总不可能把市民当挡箭牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们纯粹只是打击共和国据点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵从规则发布通告后便可从容…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 真是太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是命令 哪怕阿丽娜市再美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不得不陷入火海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不该成为军人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的避难通告！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大队各位 开始观光旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人空降了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌魔导师已和阿丽娜市的民兵汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该市现已沦陷于共和国军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无疑 我们要夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须消灭市内的所有共和国军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 严禁对非战斗人员的开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是本次城市战已许可对建筑物的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 消灭敌魔导师的前后分别进行避难通告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人接受投降固然好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不接受 则进行扫荡战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫荡战？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市战里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歼灭所有敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歼灭市内所有敌人不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算发布了通告 他们也不可能乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说还要进行炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了 民兵和非战斗人员本来就无法区分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好就是屠…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我老实点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅几个小时就来增援了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他们也知道形势紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bravo领队通知战区控制台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发送敌魔导师数据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是「莱茵的恶魔」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派了个厉害角色来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军先锋已突破防空识别线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正急速接近市区上空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备长距离伏击战！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避难通告已经发布了 这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有伏兵 我们被狙击了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员散开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人位置已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4点及7点方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让他们逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由展开近战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目的是拖时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰兹少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不知怎么的突然觉得累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮给我下兴奋剂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀斯中尉 您中弹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没发觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给您包扎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这蠢货怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有生命安危
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但应该没法继续战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀斯中尉 赶快撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是大队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了你一个人没什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想拖后腿的话带着中弹的人一起后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二指挥权移交科尼希中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二中队交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杂念太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹豫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这大蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等回去再找你算账
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌魔导师散开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持射击拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌魔导师正在后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算躲进建筑物内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 停止突击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他们打不到我们的外围炮兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的也就达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的事情就不是我管的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们再通告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知炮兵队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知所有武装的非战斗人员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秉承战时陆战条约第二十六条第三项
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求你们解放帝国市民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放不正当关押的阿丽娜市民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是真正的阿丽娜市民！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有不正当关押！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝不容许诸位的虐杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据战时陆战条约第八条第五项
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求与贵方代表官面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不接受 则视为战斗人员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群帝国畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,录到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映像已经录入宝珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发送给司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这就是没有建制的民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部通知所有部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来进行扫荡战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歼灭市内所有共和国敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 劝降通告的义务也履行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就来执行保护自国人民的任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比安特队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护共和国市民的同时撤离战区
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在救俘虏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在救人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有剩下的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是所有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知Pixie大队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当前B4区域 撤退的敌残存魔导部队正在殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友军观测班受阻 无法进行炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否可歼灭敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已目视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歼灭敌殿军之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击将重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们在五分钟内解决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您重新考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道怎么逃离炮击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们歼灭了那些魔导师的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国的敌人就会被炮击轰飞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰兹少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走的敌人会重新拿起武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了击杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果放跑了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们中就会诞生仇恨帝国的新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以就要赶尽杀绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上头的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少停火命令下达前必须开火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的蠢话我就当没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上头的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿起你的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是去年夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提交给军大学第十七研究所的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论文的论题为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何尽可能的将城市战合法化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过重新解释国际法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除对市区进行炮击的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下您是参考这篇论文立案的本次作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下官只是想确认一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论文的作者是德古雷查夫少校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校可是极其优秀的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此优秀的人才怎能不用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把解决共和国的大任交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算恢复意识了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:02.75,In,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,546)}「世界和平」医院
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身负重伤的你漂浮在峡湾上被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经持续昏迷了几个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天才刚刚确定了你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了圣光…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是神的圣光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的说法昵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神对你说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我消灭那个恶魔…

